uk.co.greedygull

Class Assets

  • Object
    • Assets
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Disposable

    public class Assets
extends Object
implements Disposable
    This class initilizes all the assets in the game as static Textures or Sounds using the constants defined in Constants.java By doing this they can be freely accessed by the rest application.
    Author:
    Matej
